    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @swistak35 this is not a bug per se but a lack in our documentation on how to track them.\n\nHere's how to do it:\n\n``` js\nvar search = instantsearch({\n  // ... other parameters\n  urlSync: {\n    trackedParameters: [\n      'attribute:*', 'query', 'page', 'hitsPerPage',\n      'aroundLatLngViaIP', 'aroundRadius'\n    ]\n  }\n});\n```\n\nYou could add more of them if needed. Seems right?\n\nThanks\n",
